org.arl.fjage.shell

Class DumbShell

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.arl.fjage.shell.DumbShell
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Shell

    public class DumbShell
extends java.lang.Object
implements Shell
    Shell input/output driver for dumb console devices (with no terminal escape sequences support). This shell is useful when dealing with machine-to-machine connections.
